<template>
  <el-header>
    <el-row type="flex" justify="space-between">
      <el-col :span="16">
        <el-menu :default-active="activeIndex" class="el-menu-demo" mode="horizontal" @select="handleSelect">
  <el-menu-item index="1">处理中心</el-menu-item>
  </el-menu>
      </el-col>
      <el-col :span="8" >
        <el-autocomplete
       class="ipt"
prefix-icon="el-icon-search"
          placeholder="请输入内容"
          @select="handleSelect"
        >
        </el-autocomplete>
        </el-col>
    </el-row>
  </el-header>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "header",
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.el-header {
  height: 230px;
  width: 100%;
  padding: auto 0;
}
.el-menu.el-menu--horizontal {
    border-bottom: none ;
}
.ipt{
  line-height: 62px;
}
.ipt input[type="text"] {
  border-radius: 1.5em;
}
</style>
